{"tid":2369255,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁海文促警嚴查郭偉强","createTime":"2021-01-17T03:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T04:53:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2548afd8ca3f8f2d2ba56ff38cf235715a192f93","tid":2369255,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:44:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/LXEQXOXBQFCSZBU4IMLA7AFMTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FLXEQXOXBQFCSZBU4IMLA7AFMTU%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=255d366f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FLXEQXOXBQFCSZBU4IMLA7AFMTU%2F&h=81aa2869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/LXEQXOXBQFCSZBU4IMLA7AFMTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n袁海文促警嚴查郭偉强<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JZG0pU5g1wz455ZxeG2QfVJ4_eo=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6NXJ7UMORFDRFDU74JMMAXBN44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJZG0pU5g1wz455ZxeG2QfVJ4_eo%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6NXJ7UMORFDRFDU74JMMAXBN44.jpg&h=8145ffc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民主黨袁海文（圓圖）指郭偉强（右圖）明顯違反交通條例。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】工聯會立法會議員郭偉强上周四於立法會房屋事務委員會進行Zoom會議期間，邊揸車邊開會，涉不小心駕駛，前天認衰兼到警署「自首」，惟警方未有披露是否收到郭偉强事件的相關舉報，民主黨深水埗區議員袁海文指郭偉强明顯違反交通條例，就此去信警務處處長鄧炳強要求嚴正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引鄧炳強「犯法就係犯法」<br />\n<br />\n根據《道路交通條例》38條，任何人士在道路上駕駛車輛時，如無適當的謹慎及專注，或未有合理顧及其他使用該道路的人，便屬不小心駕駛；袁海文稱，郭偉强邊駕駛、邊開會，明。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n袁並指，警方必須交代是否已接獲市民就相關事件的投訴或舉報；。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，郭偉强早有不小心駕駛前科。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"b48323a16f466de7b8b4b4db2e771f1521d78291","tid":2369255,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"袁海文犯國安法"},{"pid":"fbb765afe3776986f4bc8a97722047ff1be3c075","tid":2369255,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"被票控不小心駕駛 罰款3500元編輯<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員郭偉强被指在2016年6月20日，於港鐵香港大學站對出的薄扶林道路段，疑在未看清鄰線路面狀況便突然把車「抽頭」切入鄰線，結果與一輛輪椅的士相撞。當時的士上其中一名乘客是輪椅使用者，猶幸事件中無人受傷。39歲被告郭偉强昨被票控不小心駕駛罪，他在東區法院經審訊後被裁定罪成，判罰款三千五百元，並須自費修讀駕駛改進課程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條賤種唔係第一次,根本就係道路炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c85a4a35789dbd3f66eaea2ecaf4ed3da4ab5c0","tid":2369255,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:56:27.000Z","msg":"幾時拉袁海文 <br />\n已犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a50cd43cd6c57b42a30ab42897c958ff09d10f2","tid":2369255,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法，除非你係藍屍同警甴"},{"pid":"24865b219730e85f5b03a8f28393315fdb3c9b43","tid":2369255,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"而家只要係藍嘅<br />\n一係唔查<br />\n一係慢慢查"}]}